The series is about a 27-year-old lawyer with Asperger syndrome. Thanks to his high IQ of 164, impressive memory and creative thinking, brilliant Woo Young Woo graduates at the top of his class at a prestigious law school.

Number of seasons: 1 (2022)

Status: Finsihed

Channel: ENA Main

Creators: Yoo In-sik, Moon Ji-won

Starring: Eun-bin ParkTae-oh KangKang Ki-young
